title: Blondies' Bistro
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A contemporary restaurant and bar offering an international mix of American, Indian, Mexican, and Mediterranean cuisines. The health food section on the menu includes vegetarian and vegan items. In addition, some of the regular non-veg menu items can be made vegan.
